{"data":[{"date":"11:08 08/08","title":"\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau tin \u0111\u1ed3n\" xinh t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u1ed5 v\u0169 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nguoi-yeu-tin-don-xinh-tuoi-co-vu-tien-dao-van-duc-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-u23-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5238","checkdouble":"194018"},{"date":"11:11 08/08","title":"Sao MU \u0103n chay \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/sao-mu-an-chay-de-cai-thien-suc-khoe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Smalling ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c \u0103n chay gi\u00fap anh kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho MU.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trung v\u1ec7 Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf Premier League theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n chay b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Jermain Defoe c\u1ee7a Bournemouth v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal. Kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ea7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 MU kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ecbt n\u00e0o m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 to\u00e0n l\u00e0 rau, c\u1ee7, qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 h\u1ea1t. Smalling ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 Sam Cooke ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Smalling chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0103n chay.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao MU trung v\u1ec7 Smalling \u0103n chay \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao MU trung v\u1ec7 Smalling \u0103n chay \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kho\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/s1-4337-1533632518.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Smalling v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 Sam Cooke. \u1ea2nh: Instagram.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"V\u1ee3 t\u00f4i \u0103n chay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i n\u0103m nay v\u00e0 c\u00f4 \u1ea5y khuy\u00ean t\u00f4i l\u00e0m theo. C\u00f4 \u1ea5y n\u1ea5u nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n chay m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf quen d\u1ea7n. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian, t\u00f4i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ecf. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u00f3n \u0103n khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam t\u1ea5y tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i b\u1ecb vi\u00eam \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf m\u1ed7i khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0ng sau khi t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111au n\u1eefa\", Smalling chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i cho bi\u1ebft ban \u0111\u1ea7u anh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n chay m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda. Anh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf th\u1ecbt \u0111\u1ecf ra kh\u1ecfi th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0103n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ecbt kh\u00e1c. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Smalling quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0103n chay ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sau khi nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c \u0103n chay do v\u1ee3 anh cung c\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, Smalling thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn h\u01a1n. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, anh c\u00f3 46 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 10 tr\u1eadn so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016-2017. Trung v\u1ec7 MU th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0103n chay tr\u01b0\u1eddng khi\u1ebfn anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00e1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u1edf ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 hai sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t nhanh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5237","checkdouble":"194019"},{"date":"10:06 08/08","title":"Kaka chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2016/4/25/Cau-chuyen-bong-da-ve-thien-than-Kaka-cua-Brazil-va-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-5.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n Kaka chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nKaka t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng Rossoneri<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o AC Milan trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c. G\u0110KT Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c&rdquo; &ndash; Leonardo chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Kaka. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. kaka lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng Kaka s\u1ebd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd m\u1ed9t CLB &ndash; mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc l\u00e0m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t nh\u1edb n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Kaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/4/25/Cau-chuyen-bong-da-ve-thien-than-Kaka-cua-Brazil-va-AC-Milan-hinh-anh-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kaka chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc l\u00e0m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Milan, G\u0110KT Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i CLB Paolo Maldini gia nh\u1eadp h\u00e0ng ng\u0169 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng Rossoneri, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u01a1 k\u1ebd t\u00f3c, sau khi Marco Fassone v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Massimiliano Mirabelli b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i 2 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Maldini cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Leonardo \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a CLB. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chung m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i AC Milan m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p v\u00ec CLB.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo; &ndash; huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Maldini k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 CLB, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Kaka chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i AC Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111ang tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-193993.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-193993.html\">AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua bom x\u1ecbt Chelsea</span><br>\r\nAC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span><br>\r\nLeonardo Bonucci tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i khi v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Juventus sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian phi\u00eau b\u1ea1t sang AC Milan, m\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/10/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\">Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, AC Milan t\u00ednh v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 Pogba Serbia</span><br>\r\nAC Milan mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t M.U v\u00e0 Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5236","checkdouble":"193997"},{"date":"09:36 08/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park?</h2><h2><br>\r\nHLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. 2 su\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u1eefa Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 \u00edt ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00e0m &lsquo;v\u1eadt hy sinh&rsquo; \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n m\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/vanquyet_2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, kh\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 T\u00e2y n\u00e0y c\u00f2n g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i hay nh\u1eefng pha x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1c Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2014 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf trong c\u00e1c pha \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 hay tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a \u0111a s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u00e3y khoan ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n . V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup trong vai tr\u00f2 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Park r\u1ea5t bi\u1ebft nh\u00ecn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch l\u1edbn h\u01a1n cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t V-League \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 khung v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3u nhau. V\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 khung t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Duy M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng&hellip; \u0111\u00e3 \u0103n t\u1eadp v\u1edbi nhau t\u1eeb l\u00e2u n\u00ean ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3 khi \u00f4m b\u1ed9 khung c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn&nbsp; HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u nhau m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thu nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i nh\u01b0&nbsp; V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-chon-Van-Quyet,-gat-Van-Lam-Lua-chon-dung-dan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd&nbsp;l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng trong b\u1ed9 khung g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng khi m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n, tuy nhi\u00ean anh l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cao nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 9 l\u1ea7n. Do \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n &lsquo;xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc&rsquo; c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a v\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 27, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1eeba kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf trong khu v\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, \u1edf 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 106 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 43 b\u00e0n. Anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 14 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 AFF Cup 2014 v\u00e0 2016, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;r\u1eebng&rsquo; c\u0169ng t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u 6 tr\u1eadn cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xem V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft thi \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i: &ldquo;Kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c em tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o gi\u1ed1ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft Con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/82-1533604846.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 ASIAD, ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ch\u00edn ch\u1eafn, gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111a n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft. B\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch cao trong l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M\u1eb7t tr\u00e1i l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111i bu\u00f4n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 ho\u1eb7c l\u00e3i. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed9n do b\u1eadn c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Van Quyet hoi han vi pha danh nguoi voi Nghiem Xuan Tu.\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec pha \u0111\u00e1nh ngu\u1ed9i v\u1edbi Nghi\u00eam Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/29/van-quyet-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-pha-danh-nguoi-nghiem-xuan-tu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 sung s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u00e2n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. D\u1eabu sao m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u1eafn, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi bi\u1ebft tin b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-khong-bang-van-lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-168-193978.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-khong-bang-van-lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tien-dung-khong-bang-van-lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-168-193978.html\">&ldquo;Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\">HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV U23 Uzbekistan, Nuraliev Dilshod \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn <br>\r\nth\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5235","checkdouble":"193982"},{"date":"11:30 08/08","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-van-lam-bi-loai-khoi-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng tin th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng bongda24h t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Park Hang Seo.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong danh s\u00e1ch 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, &ldquo;ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o&rdquo; V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, so v\u1edbi 3 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh \u1edf 3 tuy\u1ebfn. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh, v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ra m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Olympic Uzbekistan kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Indonesia. \u00d4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Dang-Van-Lam-bi-loai-khoi-danh-sach-du-ASIAD-Ai-la-ke-that-bai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tay ngang, th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng &ndash; m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Park Hang Seo. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 s\u1ebd g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ngo\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay t\u1ea1i AFF Cup, khi Park Hang Seo c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 H\u1ed3 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, ch\u00e0ng &ldquo;th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ti\u00eau ch\u00ed n\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay v\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng &ndash; b\u1edfi Mr. Park ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdn ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u cho t\u1edbi V-League, D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, song song v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ebfm khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian, s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng Park \u01b0u \u00e1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"V\u0103n L\u00e2m vs Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/vanlamdung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e0n em \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng anh m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111i Indonesia v\u00ec &ldquo;\u0111en&rdquo;, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 v\u1edbi anh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i hy sinh v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd, v\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"V\u0103n L\u00e2m\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/vanlam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Park Hang Seo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Park c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em theo th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c, th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 quan, b\u1edfi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam phong c\u00e1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y, suy cho c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua \u1ea3nh 5\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Park Hang Seo bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>&ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo; th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong \u01b0u ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ebfm hoi t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trong khung g\u1ed7, t\u00ednh trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi ch\u00fang ta ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c ASIAD. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a, khi chi\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. D\u00f9 sao, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ed1t, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-chon-van-quyet-gat-van-lam-con-dao-hai-luoi-168-193982.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ecdn V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, g\u1ea1t V\u0103n L\u00e2m: L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang b\u00e0n t\u00e1n x\u00f4n xao v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-193979.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi bi\u1ebft tin b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5234","checkdouble":"194022"},{"date":"11:19 08/08","title":"Real th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 Juventus v\u00e0 Roma: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f3c th\u00fat th\u00edt gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfp s\u1ee3 d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Julen Lopetegui.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i nghi gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 thua Man United 1-0 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 M.U c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Real, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m trong suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i ngay, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan ng\u1ea1i s\u00e2u s\u1eafc cho Real, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Real \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U h\u00f4m 1/8 v\u1eeba qua bao g\u1ed3m Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 201819 \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 201819 \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Real-truoc-mua-201819-Dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u00e3 thua M.U 1-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n sau World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng Toni Kroos, Marco Asensio, Isco c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 77 tr\u1edf \u0111i. Real h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh C trong hi\u1ec7p 2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBao tr\u00f9m l\u00ean \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Real \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so b\u00ec trong c\u00e1c pha tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n, tr\u1ea3i qua 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" title=\"Benzema ghi ban cho Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Jose-Mourinho-nhan-xet-ve-Real-Madrid-va-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 HLV Jose Mourinho s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u00ec Real. C\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu Real thay 11 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00e2n l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u201cqu\u00e8 qu\u1eb7t\u201d l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eeba c\u01a1 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t sau 4 tr\u1eadn b\u1ebft b\u00e1t. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a \u201cC\u00e1o gi\u00e0\u201d l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng thua m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e0n, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 Bongda24h.vn ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n nh\u1eefng nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau kh\u00f3c. Ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 c\u00e1c Madridistas. H\u1ecd theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ra sao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00e0o l\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, n\u00e0o l\u00e0 v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u00f3n h\u1ecd\u2026 M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B thua \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu? N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior-180-192468.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-vinicius-junior-180-192468.html\">Thua M.U, HLV Real v\u1eabn h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Vinicius Junior. \u00d4ng khen ng\u1ee3i sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man United t\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn?</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u201ctr\u00f9 \u1ebbo\u201d Real. R\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Roma, \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng 4-2 Barcelona, ch\u00fang l\u1ea1i vang l\u00ean nheo nh\u00e9o. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 reo vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u00e0ng th\u1eadt th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 l\u1eeda. Khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o gian kh\u00f3, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Real t\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U c\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 gia v\u1ecb gi\u00fap c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb kh\u00f3c m\u01b0\u1edbn c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1m ng\u01b0ng \u201cb\u1ed5n ph\u1eadn\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 B\u1ea7y k\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n mang l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid\" title=\"Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus 3-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 AS Roma, Real \u0111\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3-1 v\u00e0 2-1, h\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ebf. C\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Real \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang t\u1edbi v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy gi\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3, trung b\u00ecnh Real ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng 65%, tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 28 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 12 l\u00e0 \u0111i tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 43%. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real vs Roma Asensio ghi ban\" title=\"Real vs Roma Asensio ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Real-vs-Roma-Asensio-ghi-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Roma v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee9 m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n Real t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u1ede gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, Los Blancos c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c hay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Luka Modric ch\u01b0a t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u1ede hai c\u00e1nh, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Marco Asensio, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ch\u1ea1m l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u00e0 Roma, c\u1ea3 Bale v\u00e0 Asensio \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Real m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean khi 5 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Bale v\u00e0 Asensio v\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 3 v\u00e0 2. N\u1ebfu Karim Benzema b\u00e9n duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n, Real s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale toa sang tai Real\" title=\"Bale toa sang tai Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Bale-toa-sang-tai-Real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gareth Bale ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi 50 b\u00e0n/ m\u00f9a nh\u01b0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m. HLV Lopetegui c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t Ronaldo m\u1edbi b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb Real ng\u1eebng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Eden Hazard khi Chelsea h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal c\u1ee7a Lopetegui kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch t\u00f4n vinh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0o, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Real ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Juventus v\u00e0 Roma l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma, khi c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111a ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0o), h\u1ecd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thang Roma\" title=\"Real Madrid thang Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/real-truoc-mua-201819-dau-roi-nhung-ke-khoc-muon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Real tung ra v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Roma trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 5 l\u00e0 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i s\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m b\u00ean kia thay v\u00ec d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. C\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i g\u00ec h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa \u1edf Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19 sau c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu? N\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft v\u1eabn r\u01a1i, n\u1ebfu v\u1eabn c\u00f2n than van, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 xem. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 cho tinh th\u1ea7n thi\u1ebfu cao th\u01b0\u1ee3ng!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Real tr\u01b0\u1edbc Roma:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/8/Real-2-1-Roma.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5233","checkdouble":"194020"},{"date":"10:44 08/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Arsenal chia tay th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/arsenal-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-chambers.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Calum Chambers \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Chambers r\u1eddi Arsenal\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Arsenal chia tay trung v\u1ec7 Chambers h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Arsenal chia tay trung v\u1ec7 Chambers h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/CHINH-THUC-Arsenal-chia-tay-trung-ve-Chambers-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chambers r\u1eddi Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chambers l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Southampton v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016/17 \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Middlesbrough tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Arsenal m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Chambers ra s\u00e2n 12 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1i Premier League trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 HLV Wenger t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/calum-chambers-43861.html\" target=\"_blank\">Calum Chambers</span> v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Fulham \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chambers h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, Chambers cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Fulham r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Fulham l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ng\u1eafn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u00edch. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Fulham \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh kh\u00e1 danh ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri, Aleksandar Mitrovic v\u00e0 Andre Schurrle. Chambers l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Fulham sau khi Alfie Mawson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Slavisa Jokanovic s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u1edf Premier League b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 7 tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Fulham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o top 10 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-se-giup-arsenal-tro-lai-top-4-172-194001.html\">Emery s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Arsenal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-hang-thai-tien-gan-toi-canh-cua-roi-arsenal-172-193989.html\">2 \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5232","checkdouble":"194012"},{"date":"10:54 08/08","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U nh\u1eafm Boateng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 MU mua Jerome Boateng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Co-hoi-de-MU-mua-Jerome-Boateng-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina t\u1eeb Barca b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i va ch\u1ea1m c\u1ee7a Boateng gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Boateng b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/that-bai-vu-mina-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-nguoi-thay-the-172-193829.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Jerome Boateng</span> \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jerome Boateng\" title=\"Jerome Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0608-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U v\u00ec Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Mouirnho, anh c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBoateng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n Mourinho v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac. \u00d4ng n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Boateng, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bayern quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5231","checkdouble":"194013"},{"date":"11:15 08/08","title":"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o \u1edf Arsenal khi\u1ebfn HLV Emery lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/vi-tri-nao-o-arsenal-khien-hlv-emery-lo-lang-nhat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Arsenal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Trong Top 7 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed3i nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 51 b\u00e0n thua.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/vi-tri-nao-o-arsenal-khien-hlv-emery-lo-lang-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 \u1edf Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 trung v\u1ec7 m\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111ang c\u00f3, \u00f4ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua trung v\u1ec7\u00a0m\u1edbi. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Sokratis t\u1eeb Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Sokratis t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Ruhr, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 n\u1eefa</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Arsenal l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y lo ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jerome Boateng\" title=\"Jerome Boateng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/ngay-hom-nay-88.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jerome Boateng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Laurent Koscielny \u0111ang d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-chambers-172-194012.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal chia tay Calum Cham</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Mustafi, Sokratis, Rob Holding v\u00e0 Konstantinos Mavropanos, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal quan t\u00e2m Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u1edbn. Domagoj Vida c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m, Besiktas \u0111\u00f2i 29 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch mua s\u1eafm, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00f4ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n b\u1edbt m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Welbeck, Ospina v\u00e0 Lucas Perez l\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i cao nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5230","checkdouble":"194014"},{"date":"11:12 08/08","title":"HLV Lyon m\u1eddi m\u1ecdc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia mua Nabil Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/lyon-de-ngo-kha-nang-ban-nabil-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir. Ch\u00ednh HLV Bruno Genesio \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fekir \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, Nabil Fekir thi\u1ebfu ch\u00fat n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u00e0 Lyon v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd v\u00e0 r\u00fat kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c Fekir \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn cho Lyon ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng b\u00e1n. Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Man United v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ligue 1 mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/lyon-de-ngo-kha-nang-ban-nabil-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lyon \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Fekir ra \u0111i b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLyon m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau khi h\u00f2a 0-0 \u1edf 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh. Sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Bruno Genesio c\u1ee7a \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc li\u1ec7u Fekir c\u00f3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i \u1edf m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. Ai m\u00e0 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra? C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Fekir v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/boateng-tu-choi-mu-vi-mourinho-172-194013.html\">Sao kh\u1ee7ng tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU v\u00ec Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-khang-dinh-se-khong-mua-them-nguoi-172-194007.html\">Pep kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jan-oblak-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-chelsea-172-194006.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-alderweireld-an-dut-maguire-172-194004.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Alderweireld \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t Maguire</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5229","checkdouble":"194015"},{"date":"11:29 08/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 08/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/8/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-0808.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 08/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0808 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0808 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0808-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea-172-193991.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0808-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea-172-193991.html\">Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Jan Oblak th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, theo El Correo c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zouma</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Bakayoko</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>N\u00f3ng: Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Kepa\" title=\"thu mon Kepa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/chelsea-muon-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Kepa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Batshuayi Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sevilla mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Michy Batshuayi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/2/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea cho Nantes m\u01b0\u1ee3n Matt Miazga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb The Blues.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian va Mourinho\" title=\"Willian va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Willian-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Mourinho \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi The Blues. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u1ee5 sao Aston Villa</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish, ng\u00f4i sao c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Spurs \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t The Blues trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m &quot;h\u00e0ng hot&quot; Bundesliga</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leon Bailey n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5228","checkdouble":"194021"},{"date":"07:18 08/08","title":"Chelsea 0-0 (pen 5-4) Lyon: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/chelsea-00-lyon-pen-54-chien-thang-nhoc-nhan-tren-cham-luan-luu-11m.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i ICC 2018, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Lyon c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0 sau 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-4 nh\u1edd c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: CHELSEA 0-0 (PEN 5-4) LYON\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/8/CHELSEA-VS-LYON.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111ang l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Chelsea su\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua. Thibaut Courtois d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid c\u00f2n Chelsea t\u00ednh chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Kepa Arrizabalaga. Trong khi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea m\u00f9a t\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh th\u00ec 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Marcin Bulka v\u00e0 Rob Green \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap The Blues c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i ICC 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb Bulka \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Maurizio Sarri cho b\u1eaft ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Lyon. Ph\u00fat 26, Bulka \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Memphis Depay. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ha Lan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i r\u1ed3i tung c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda g\u00f3c xa. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Bulka \u0111\u00e3 bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng c\u1ee9u thua cho Chelsea.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Chelsea vs Lyon 0-0 pen 5-4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt Chelsea vs Lyon 0-0 pen 5-4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Ket-qua-tuong-thuat-Chelsea-vs-Lyon-0-0-pen-5-4-tran-dau-ICC-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Green l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 34, Depay l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u01a1i m\u00e0o m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Chelsea. Depay ch\u1ecdc khe cho Houssem Aouar l\u1ecdt xu\u1ed1ng v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Bulka. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Aouar l\u1ea1i \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc. B\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, Lyon \u0111\u00e0nh ra ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HLV Sarri l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tung nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Jorginho, N'Golo Kante, Olivier Giroud hay Eden Hazard v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Lyon v\u00e0 The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Green \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Pape Diop \u1edf lo\u1ea1t th\u1ee9 5. D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Hazard \u0111\u00e3 s\u00fat th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a 11m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Lyon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u<br>\r\nChelsea: Bulka (Green 74'); Zappacosta (Azpilicueta 74'), Christensen (Cahill 74'), Ampadu (Ruediger 74'), Emerson (Alonso 74'); Bakayoko (Jorginho 59'), Drinkwater (Kante 59'), Loftus-Cheek (Barkley 59'); Moses (Piazon 68'), Willian (Hazard 68'), Abraham (Giroud 68')<br>\r\nLyon: Lopes; Dubois (Rafael 66'), Marcelo, Morel, Mendy; NDombele (Diop 66'), Tousart, Aouar (Ferri 79'); Traore (Gouiri 86'), Diaz (Terrier 65'), Depay (Tete 79')<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5227","checkdouble":"193990"},{"date":"07:28 08/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Everton mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. </strong>Everton \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Manchester United v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona song t\u1edbi nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U. </strong>Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u1ee7a Man United r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Barca theo giao k\u00e8o c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Tien-ve-Paul-Pogba-tro-lai-MU-sau-ky-nghi-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Bakayoko. </strong>AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1eeb Chelsea. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 \u1edf Monaco. Anh hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Maurizio Sarri b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nCandreva t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Inter.</strong> Antonio Candreva \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Inter Milan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 31 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Monaco. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng Keita Balde \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Lazio.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch sao tr\u1ebb Anh 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a BBC, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish. Spurs hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam 9/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" title=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/5-thuong-vu-sap-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ky-chuyen-nhuong-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Chirivella chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Liverpool. </strong>Celtic hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Pedro Chirivella v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y, Rosenborg \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng Chirivella th\u00ec l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Na Uy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal tung chi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Dembele khi\u1ebfn Barca ng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda.</strong> Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Barca. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mu\u1ed9n Dembele trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 9 c\u1ee7a West Ham \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Arsenal?</strong> Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Sky Sports kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5226","checkdouble":"193992"}]}